### 4 — `popup/popup.html` — New iframe UI controls

#### [MODIFY] [popup.html](file:///m:/.systemfile/webpage-content-extractor-extension/popup/popup.html)

Add two new `form-group` blocks **below** the Algorithm selector:

```html
<!-- Extract From (shown only when current tab has iframes) -->
<div class="form-group" id="iframe-source-group" style="display:none;">
  <label for="iframe-source-select">Extract From</label>
  <select id="iframe-source-select" class="select-input">
    <option value="main">Main Document Only</option>
    <option value="iframes">Iframes Only</option>
    <option value="both">Main + Iframes</option>
  </select>
</div>

<!-- Iframe Picker (shown when source = iframes or both) -->
<div class="form-group" id="iframe-picker-group" style="display:none;">
  <label style="margin-bottom:5px;display:block;">Select Iframes</label>
  <div id="iframe-picker-list"
       style="max-height:130px;overflow-y:auto;border:1px solid var(--border-color);
              border-radius:4px;padding:4px;background:var(--surface-color);">
    <div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--text-muted);padding:5px;">Loading…</div>
  </div>
  <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--text-muted);margin-top:3px;">
    No selection = use first iframe
  </div>
</div>
```

