### 7 — `content/sidebar.ts` & `content/chatbot_injector.ts` — Sub-frame guard

#### [MODIFY] [sidebar.ts](file:///m:/.systemfile/webpage-content-extractor-extension/content/sidebar.ts)

Add at the very top of the IIFE:

```ts
if (window !== window.top) return; // Don't run sidebar inside iframes
```

#### [MODIFY] [chatbot_injector.ts](file:///m:/.systemfile/webpage-content-extractor-extension/content/chatbot_injector.ts)

Add at the bootstrap section:

```ts
if (window !== window.top) { /* skip */ return; }
```

This prevents the sidebar and injector UI from being injected into every sub-frame now that `all_frames: true` is set.

