## Verification Plan

| Test | Expected |
|---|---|
| Page with no iframes | `iframe-source-group` stays hidden; extraction identical to before |
| Page with same-origin iframe | Group appears; `iframes` mode extracts iframe content correctly |
| Page with cross-origin iframe (e.g. YouTube embed) | Group appears; cross-origin frame is listed; extraction works because content script is injected into the iframe |
| Nested iframes (2 levels) | Hierarchical labels render correctly (`main > iframe-0 > iframe-0`) |
| `both` mode | Output has `=== Main Document ===` and `=== Frame: ... ===` sections |
| Default (no iframe selected) | First frame in list is used automatically |
| Sidebar not injected into sub-frames | No `wce-ai-sidebar-container` appears inside iframe DOM |
| Chatbot injector — Extract & Insert with `iframes` | Content from first iframe inserted into chatbot input |
| Firefox build | Same behaviour; `webNavigation` permission accepted |
